{"tid":1149631,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米「雷長老」現身印度分店","createTime":"2019-05-11T09:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T02:22:55.000Z","uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3623c1d30d790d35f6810905e6c477e76fb77eac","tid":1149631,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"05月11日(六)<br />\n<br />\n財經<br />\n絲絲講場：小米「雷長老」現身印度分店<br />\n   <br />\n小米雷軍身穿傳統印度服裝，造型都幾盞鬼！<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHZ4NH3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHZ4NH3.jpg&h=06e66bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前小米專賣店Mi Studio喺印度班加羅爾（Bangalore）正式開業，小米（01810）董事長雷軍就去咗當地參加開業儀式，仲入鄉隨俗，着埋傳統印度服裝，造型盞鬼。唔怪得知有網民直呼佢一聲「雷長老」，仲話小米喺印度本地化活動係由佢帶領。<br />\n雷軍仲喺微博發表咗張相話：「剛在印度參加了一家Mi Studio開業。招牌右邊是漢言拼音Xiaomi，左邊是當地語言寫的Xiaomi，據悉印度常用的有十多種地方語言。」<br />\n另外，雷總仲Post咗張喺小米印度總部見到嘅奇景，相入面係由小米印度團隊，用9,590個燈泡砌成嘅巨大小米Logo，此舉仲入咗健力士世界紀錄！<br />\n續推物聯網產品<br />\n講番小米喺印度嘅市場，公司依家係當地排名第一嘅智能電話、智能電視同智能手環嘅品牌，其中，小米手機原來已經進軍咗印度五年咁耐！而喺過去兩年，小米亦成功壓過三星，榮登印度智能手機出貨量冠軍，相信未來仲會喺印度推出更多嘅物聯網（IoT）產品。"},{"pid":"895e97b190c35e1d01487b14fe4a9948292c5d2e","tid":1149631,"uid":225846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c466cdf02d251f6819c14d8ba8d8baa5157014e","tid":1149631,"uid":74913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"搵個蝗嚟著咖哩衫好明顯係辱咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6585ebc3650938469f2868d78aa33429d57f040b","tid":1149631,"uid":74913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"搵個蝗嚟著咖哩衫好明顯係辱咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e111d06c196aa9582d6f8f9100cc9008d2715c7f","tid":1149631,"uid":131690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"屌，成個三哥咁款，笑到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528e9c9e8f1373074cae9922001fe42b629e69fa","tid":1149631,"uid":199642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"牙祖咁樣"},{"pid":"8347bd97445d50e0bca1d02c37d3f9b21e389024","tid":1149631,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"佢首are you ok mix好好丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ea03710d52125e17462379810ec02f0276478e","tid":1149631,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}